title: Experience perfectly modeled Jacksonville Bridges in MSFS!
description:
In this video we will look at a package from RKBridger which elevates and updates the bridges in de Jacksonville (Florida) area. This package will make MSFS even more realistic since currently a lot of the bridges are under the water.

For a full overview of items added to the marketplace this week have a look at the video below:
